Date: Mon, 17 Sep 2018 09:22:56 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] net: stmmac: Rework coalesce timer and fix multi-queue races
References: bnc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 4.18.15
Git-commit: 8fce3331702316d4bcfeb0771c09ac75d2192bbc

[ Upstream commit 8fce3331702316d4bcfeb0771c09ac75d2192bbc ]

This follows David Miller advice and tries to fix coalesce timer in
multi-queue scenarios.

We are now using per-queue coalesce values and per-queue TX timer.

Coalesce timer default values was changed to 1ms and the coalesce frames
to 25.

Tested in B2B setup between XGMAC2 and GMAC5.

